247
00:16:56,567 --> 00:16:57,991
Cammina lungo l'asse.

248
00:17:03,413 --> 00:17:04,775
Ehi! Aspetta!

249
00:17:06,793 --> 00:17:07,793
No, fermo!

250
00:17:20,004 --> 00:17:21,491
